WARNING!!! these instructions have not been completed, don't complain if they don't work for you
================================================================================================

Build instructions:

OS X

Make sure you have Xcode installed, you can get it from Apple: http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/xcode/id497799835?mt=12

1 - Set up Git and configure GitHub [http://help.github.com/mac-set-up-git/]

2 - Clone the repository:
    - Open the terminal and execute the following commands:
    - Go to the folder where you want the prototype folder to be created
        cd /path/to/directory
    - Clone the repo:
        git clone git://github.com/AXR/Prototype.git

3 - Download and install all required libraries:

    - Boost:
        http://www.boost.org/users/download/

    - Qt:
        http://qt-project.org/downloads

4 - Open the Xcode project (prototype/mac/AXR Test App.xcodeproj) and hit Run



Windows: coming soon...
